{"text": " We don't talk about Bruno, no, no, no, no, but lies beyond. This came about as a way to connect and bring down barriers, especially between Disney animation and the deaf community. People think that deaf people and music don't mix, but that's actually not true and quite the opposite is true. Deaf people have been singing since day one. We looked at the movie, we looked at the song many, many times, we looked at the lyrics and broke those down and then we developed translations with the actors and then marked those translations, rehearsed with the actors, came into the filming room and then filmed each movement, each camera angle and had to work through what works and what doesn't work on every shot. I actually feel that it's just going to open up other possibilities that maybe haven't been thought of yet. And everything will never be the same again.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 0.0, "end": 8.32, "text": " We don't talk about Bruno, no, no, no, no, but lies beyond.", "tokens": [50364, 492, 500, 380, 751, 466, 23046, 11, 572, 11, 572, 11, 572, 11, 572, 11, 457, 9134, 4399, 13, 50780], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2481602972204035, "compression_ratio": 1.5971563981042654, "no_speech_prob": 0.1398075968027115}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 8.32, "end": 14.84, "text": " This came about as a way to connect and bring down barriers, especially between Disney", "tokens": [50780, 639, 1361, 466, 382, 257, 636, 281, 1745, 293, 1565, 760, 13565, 11, 2318, 1296, 8653, 51106], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2481602972204035, "compression_ratio": 1.5971563981042654, "no_speech_prob": 0.1398075968027115}, {"id": 2, "seek": 0, "start": 14.84, "end": 17.92, "text": " animation and the deaf community.", "tokens": [51106, 9603, 293, 264, 15559, 1768, 13, 51260], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2481602972204035, "compression_ratio": 1.5971563981042654, "no_speech_prob": 0.1398075968027115}, {"id": 3, "seek": 0, "start": 17.92, "end": 22.